      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHREWD ETHICS (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 19.35 beating CALYPSO ETHICS. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. The hardest to beat again. FANCY LENA (7) has a strong record this trip with four wins and two placings from nine starts. Was out of placings last time (19.79) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. Can feature in the finish. CANYA SUPERSONIC (4) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her exceptional win the start prior, getting around this track over 340m in 19.05. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. CALYPSO ETHICS (8) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.",
